<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_271_r1l2">Wir ~ die <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> deʒ Rats <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒü <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> <expan>offenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> mit <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> brıef </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l3">daʒ für vns <expan>köme<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt Hans <expan>Lange<ex>n</ex>felder</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd hat vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l4">fürgeleget / vvie Jm Acht tüch genomen würden / <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Jm der <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l5">veſt / Erhart <expan>vorſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>cʒu<ex>m</ex></expan> Newenhaws ſechs tüch vvider geſchıckt hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l6">vnd hat vor vns cʒü den <expan>heilıge<ex>n</ex></expan> behabt / daʒ <expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Acht tüch ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l7">vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>g<ex>er</ex></expan> ſein / Alſo / daʒ kein awſman <expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> teil noch gemein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l8">daran nicht hab / . vnd die ſechs tüch ſein Jm <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vörſt<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l9"><expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als er vns geſagt vnd <expan>gepet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / das vvir darumb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l10">der die <expan>diſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſechs tüch <expan>eingenome<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ſich <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>wunden</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
