<ab facs="#facs_271_r1l15">Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıg<ex>elt</ex></expan> mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
